#`{md
## auth-response

Inherits api-response's functionality

- .auth-response: returns a successful auth response's key, otherwise an empty string
}
class auth-response is api-response {
  has $!key;
  submethod BUILD(:$!key, *@_, *%_) {nextsame}

  method key(--> Str) { $!key//'' }
}
